      "date": "2026-05-19",
      "title": "PEEK: Context Map as an Orientation Cache for Long-Context LLM Agents",
      "topic": "agent",
      "language": [
        "zh",
        "en"
      ],
      "authors": [
        "Zhuohan Gu",
        "Qizheng Zhang",
        "Omar Khattab",
        "Samuel Madden"
      ],
      "institution": "OpenAI, MIT",
      "summary": {
        "zh": "PEEK 的价值在于把长期上下文 Agent 的记忆问题，从“多保留历史”转成“维护可复用上下文地图”，这让它在重复访问同一外部知识环境时更高效，也更接近真正可运维的 Agent 记忆机制。",
        "en": "PEEK reframes long-context agent memory as maintaining a reusable map of the environment instead of merely preserving more history, which makes the proposal operationally compelling for repeated same-context workloads."
      },
